{
  "stem": "19211.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard of a lot of killings, taking Jews to the woods and shooting them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't want to go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From the ghettos they were taking them, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's why we went into hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was in 1942, '43, maybe '43.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why we couldn't be free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We couldn't be-- we didn't have the freedom then to be outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were not allowed to show ourselves outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, they would shoot you on sight-- that if they saw you-- any Jewish people outside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw my friend from school, from that Tarbut school, she got shot and her brother and her father.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saw it through a--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was in 1943 or '44, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in the hiding by a farmer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were hiding us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next house was another farmer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other family was hiding there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day, they SS and Ukrainian police came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took them out in the yard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they shot them right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were in another hiding place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember one thing-- that this SS came down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had-- our hiding place was, like, dug on the floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were going into a little stable, where they had a cow there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they divided that stable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's difficult to explain, but we were hiding there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That SS man, after the killings that he did, he came to the-- I saw his boots in that little hall that he came.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Until today, I don't know-- I-- whether he was decent or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He knew we were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he screamed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He said, nobody is here!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He gave a scream to the others.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they believed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
